{
  "stem": "9601.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't know if it was by design or by accident or something, his big straw stack-- you know, when after threshing, you got to do something with it-- stood here, right by the barn.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he had a hiding place in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You know what a fence, a fence, you know, they had wooden fences, maybe 4 feet, 5 feet tall.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "When they threw the straw, all the straw stayed on top of that fence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But the fence became a lean-to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So under this fence, there was a hole.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He must have known about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "That's where we crawled into.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we stayed there the winter of '42.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Ach, what a drafty place that was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was also on a hill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So I think there's something to do with the air currents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And if it's a straight hole, it was terrible, and it was drafty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There was never a warm day there, never.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He even had hired help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "That's how well he was off, Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Dvorak.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And Tante Chaika was with us, and I used to sleep next to Tante Chaika.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So when she turned her back on me, it was toasty warm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "When she turned the other way, I was cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "My brother slept with-- near my parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was always cold, always hungry, always thirsty, and always cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we stayed there the winter till about November, December, something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then one day, you know, he had hired help?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he had dogs also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of the dogs got the smell of us, and he used to come to the hole and bark and bark.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, we used to throw him food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, my father used to get to the hole there and throw him out a few pieces of bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
